PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ?spouse WHERE {
  dbr:Johann_Heinrich_Appel dbo:child ?child .
  ?child dbo:spouse ?spouse .
  dbr:Louis_IV,_Grand_Duke_of_Hesse dbo:successor ?successor .
  dbr:Louis_II,_Grand_Duke_of_Hesse dbo:predecessor ?predecessor .
  ?successor rdfs:label ?successorLabel .
  ?predecessor rdfs:label ?predecessorLabel .
  FILTER (lang(?successorLabel) = "en" && lang(?predecessorLabel) = "en")
}

question: Give me the spouse of the native, that is a politician, of Poltava Governorate.
generated_sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>

SELECT ?spouse WHERE {
  ?politician a dbo:Politician .
  ?politician dbo:birthPlace dbr:Poltava_Governorate .
  ?politician dbo:spouse ?spouse .
}
